. This volume presents various ways to put construction works out to tender. In addition, it explains in practical terms how to describe construction work and how to prepare all of the documentation required for a complete invitation to tender.Subjects: Allocating construction work; Different ways to specify construction work; The structure of a work specification; Quantity determination; Using invitations to tender to realize plan quality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAusschreibung. 4aBauleistung. 4aBauvorhaben. 4aBerufspraxis. 4aFachlos. 4aGebäudequalität. 4aGewerk. 4aLehrbuch Architektur. 4aLehrbücher Architektur. 4aLeistungsbeschreibung. 4aLeistungspaket. 4aLeistungsposition. 4aLeistungsumfang. 4aProjektleitung. 4aProjektmanagement. 4aStudentenreihe Basics. 4aStudienliteratur Architektur. 4aTeillos. 4aVergabe. 4aVergabeeinheit. 4aZeichnungselement. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh1 aFranssen, Sebastian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBASICS ONLINE PAKET DEUTSCHz9783035611649oZDB-23-BON08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA0 cEPUBz97830356118230 cprintz978303821518940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303561265340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035612653423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035612653/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-BON  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014